{"id": "ke-near-1", "target": "kit-extender", "kind": "near-miss-negative", "prompt": "Add a helper function to our public API so callers can paginate results.", "expectation": "Must NOT route to kit-extender. Correct target: implementer — building product code, not authoring .claude/ kit components."}
{"id": "ke-near-2", "target": "kit-extender", "kind": "near-miss-negative", "prompt": "Write a usage guide for our end users explaining how to configure the CLI.", "expectation": "Must NOT route to kit-extender. Correct target: documentation — human-facing product docs, not extending the kit's components."}
