{"id": "obs-pos-1", "target": "observability", "kind": "positive", "prompt": "Define the service-level objectives and an error budget for the checkout flow, and decide which signals we should track to know it's healthy.", "expectation": "Routes to observability: deciding WHAT to measure — SLOs, error budgets, the signals/SLIs — Operations measurement that begins in Construction."}
